\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh no. No, no, no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 That was left to your mother entirely?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Yes. Yes. Yes. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 You didn't help with the children at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Did you have to do anything for your elder brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Did they expect any of you to do anything for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh no, no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
