\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Do you remember any occasions you ever ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh no, no, no.
