\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Do you know if your mother would bake her own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh no. No, she didn't bake her own. Well bread was so cheap - cheap them days, I can't remember now what it was but I know - always go out 
and get a loaf of bread, or two loaves of bread or how many she required.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 What about jam making, would she ever make her own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Yes. Yes. Yes, she very often made jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Would she get the fruit from the markets or something like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh yes, yes, it was quite cheap.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 What about bottling fruit or vegetables or making pickles, did she do anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh yes, she used to to - cucumbers - she used to pickle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Would she ever make any wine or any beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Yes. Yes, yes. She used to make mead - mead. Mead. And it was wonderful, marvellous.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 What was it made out of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 I - that I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Honey isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Yes, I think so. Yes, yes. Mm. Very very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Would she keep that specially for visitors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Mostly she used to make it mostly Passover.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 What about medicines, would she make up any of her own medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 She'd buy cough mixtures and this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh yes, yes, we'd go to the chemist and buy it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 In your sort of garden out the back did you grow any fruit or vegetables at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Only - only some runner beans. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Would your parents buy fruit and vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh yes, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 What about tinned fruit or tinned vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Tinned vegetables there was hardly - tinned vegetables about them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 What about dried fruit or vegetables?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Prunes. Prunes and all that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 You would have that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh - oh yes, yes, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Did you keep any livestock of any sort?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Yes, my father used to keep chickens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Out the back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Would they be for eating or just as sort of pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Well, that I would - that I wouldn't know, I think it was more for eating, but I suppose used to sell some as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Perhaps he enjoyed}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587160\charrsid209760  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 it as a hobby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Mm. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 He didn't keep rabbits or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 How many times a week do you think you'd eat meat in your family, do you think it was quite often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 That I couldn't say, I couldn't say. I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Do you ever remember eating tinned meat of any sort?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 There wasn't much tinned stuff about them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Do you ever remember seeing your mother having less food so the rest of her family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 No. No. No. Didn't - didn't apply.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Did your father get extra because he was the breadwinner, would he be given anything special to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Well - I mean, a man gets a man's meal, a woman - always eats less.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Were the children allowed to talk during meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh of course they were. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to eat a bit of everything on the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh we had - we had to eat - what was on the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 What was your parents attitude if you left some food uneaten on the plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Well we - we - we never left anything, we always ate it.
