t until it was offered to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Well - I can't remember, I just don't remember, it's no good me saying -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 What about second helpings, were you allowed to ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 That I wouldn't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 And sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Were you allowed to bring toys or books to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Your parents didn't mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 If you were playing with something they let you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh yes, yes, sure.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 When were you allowed to leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Yes, when we finished our dinner.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Did you have to wait for everybody to finish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 As soon as you'd finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 You could go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Did you all sit down at the same time for the meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8133147 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Yes. Yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10036353 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4859080\charrsid209760 Did you have the same place each time?
